               <date type="single-match" when="1796-08-12">
                  <anchor type="date"/>
                  <seg type="date-jy" subtype="v-mk">cārvati <g facs="#yj1c">YJ1c</g></seg>
                  <seg type="date-sm" subtype="v-mk">vaiyyāci <abbr type="abbr" facs="#m"
                     >m°</abbr></seg>
                  <seg type="date-md" subtype="v-mk"><num type="digit-o">30</num>
                     <g facs="#d2">D2</g></seg>
                  <seg type="date-wd" subtype="v-mk">veḷḷikiḻamaiyum</seg>
                  <seg type="date-n" subtype="v-mk">uttiranaṣcattiramum</seg>
                  <seg type="date-t" subtype="v"><num type="word-o">cattamiyum</num></seg>
                  <seg type="date-o" subtype="v-mk" n="laksana">kaṟkkāṭalakkaṇamum</seg> yippaṭi<lb type="2"
                     n="114v2"/>p paṭṭa <orig>cupataṉattil</orig> (emend into cupatiṉattil) </date>
               <anchor type="scribe"/>
               <seg type="pers"
                  subtype="scribe"><persName role="father">kōvaḷam tāṉappaceṭṭiyār</persName> kumāraṉ 
                  <persName role="scribe">kaṭaikuṭṭi mutticeṭṭi</persName></seg>
               <anchor type="item"/>
               <seg type="copItem" subtype="title">vaḷḷiyammaipurāṇam</seg>
               <anchor type="copFor"/>
               <seg type="copFor-end" subtype="eḻuti-muṟṟ">eḻuti niṟain<lb type="2" n="114v3"/>tutu
                  muṟṟum</seg> &#xBF3; </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>On the auspicious day (°taṉattil, emend into °tiṉattil) in which so occur the Jovian
               year Cārvati, the month of Vaiyyāci, the 30th day, Friday, the constellation of
               Uttiram, the seventh [lunar day] and the lakkaṇam Kaṟkkāṭa, Kaṭaikuṭṭi Mutticeṭṭi son
               of Kōvaḷam Tāṉappaceṭṭiyār fully copied and completed the Vaḷḷiyammaipurāṇam. The
               teacher is the refuge, we need Vaḷḷiṉāyakiyammai to protect (raṣcuttuk kāṟkka)
               [us].</p>
         </div>
